name: Primary Colors Birthday Set
description:
The perfect set to celebrate a pretend birthday. You will receive two slices of birthday cake each with a removable candle that is attached with velcro, one pink cupcake, one blue cupcake and two frosted and sprinkled cookies.

Cake slices measure approx 5" long and 2" high
Cupcakes measures approx 2" in diameter and 4" high from base to top of icing.
Cookies measure approx 3" in diameter
